{"tid":669743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停職警深水埗店擸$32貨 涉盜竊被捕","createTime":"2018-05-18T17:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T18:36:47.000Z","uid":184465,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d510b1be39aa64f408bf4ea145bc192729bbbc2","tid":669743,"uid":184465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:10:22.000Z","msg":"停職警知法犯法，涉盜竊被捕！下午4時許，一名51歲姓張男子在深水埗福華街一商舖內，被職員發現懷疑盜去4件合共32元的貨物。剛巧此時有警員巡經現場，職員於是報案，其後警方經調查後，以涉嫌「盜竊」把張拘捕，帶署扣留調查。案件由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後得知，被捕男子為一名停職警員，因涉及另一宗案件，於多年前被停職。<span style=\"color: orange;\">警方強調非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53389e04bddd5f0a97fc1675fc2adcf5d4959ab0","tid":669743,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"一睇就知佢唔係做開大事既人"},{"pid":"c1f2abb6489f69a5fbd9e8fe51b0564ccb96847b","tid":669743,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd37173f93907402b30db56d3fc3e5669e452aa","tid":669743,"uid":10890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"屌你冇大志就真係冇大志<br />\n偷野都偷得嗰32蚊"},{"pid":"76b96397dec12e735c410fcf283208246ef88d61","tid":669743,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T18:11:55.000Z","msg":"又係特賣城？<br />\n<br />\n間野都幾好野成日拉到人"},{"pid":"a48dbf829bdb00096a76eba31d2687b72a2573ab","tid":669743,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T18:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}